COMPANY DESCRIPTION\
--------------------\
If you know you should be posting on social media but never seem to\
find the time, All Ways Posted was built for exactly that problem.\
We're a done-for-you social media content posting service for small\
businesses. Every month we create 20 on-brand posts matched to your\
business \'97 your colors, your voice, your style \'97 and deliver five of\
them to you every Friday, ready to go.\
\
We're not a social media marketing agency. We don't run ads, chase\
followers, or make promises about growing your business. We do one\
thing: keep your feed consistent, professional, and active so you\
never have to think about it. Your brand stays visible while you focus\
on running the actual business.\
\
Month-to-month. No contracts. Starting at $497/month.\
Cancel anytime with one week's notice.\
