IDEAL CUSTOMER PROFILE\
-----------------------\
The ideal All Ways Posted client is a local service business owner or\
licensed professional who is actively running their business. Think:\
the salon owner behind the chair 40 hours a week. The gym owner on\
the floor with clients every morning. The realtor juggling 6 active\
listings. The dentist between patients all day.\
\
They are typically solo operators or small teams of 2-10 people.\
In business at least 1-2 years. Real customer base. Functioning\
website. They have revenue, they have clients, and they have a\
business worth representing online.\
\
They already know social media matters. The problem is not awareness\
\'97 it's execution. They start posting, get busy, fall off, feel guilty,\
and the cycle repeats. They do not want a marketing lecture. They want\
the problem gone.\
\
IN ONE LINE: A busy, successful small business owner who knows they\
should be posting, hates that they aren't, and just wants someone to\
make the problem disappear for $497 a month.\
